==English==
===Etymology===
Borrowed from German ''[[Nazi#German|Nazi]]''.

===Noun===
'''Nazi''' (plural: '''[[Nazis]]''')

#(''proper noun'') A member of the German National Socialist party ([[NSDAP]]), a political organization headed by Adolf Hitler in the early 20th century.
#(''proper noun'') A person subscribing to the doctrines of the German Nazi party.


